'''Hind Bensari''' (  yavutse 1987), ni umukinnyi wa firime wa [[Maroke|Maroc]]<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm9632189/</ref> .   Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wakoze firime ya documentaire yamamaye cyane: ''475: Break the Silence'' na ''We Could Be Heroes''<ref>https://www.festivalmarrakech.info/en/personnalite/hind-bensari/</ref> . 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1987 i Casablanca, muri [[Maroke|Maroc]] . Icyakora akiri muto cyane, yimukiye i Londres.<ref>https://www.tfiny.org/filmmakers/detail/hind_bensari</ref>  Bensari yahawe impamyabumenyi mu by'ubukungu no mu burasirazuba bwo hagati yakuye muri kaminuza ya Edinburgh <ref>https://womenandhollywood.com/hot-docs-2018-women-directors-meet-hind-bensari-we-could-be-heroes-c09906f8505e/</ref>. Afite kandi impamyabumenyi mu bukungu mpuzamahanga bwa politiki yakuye mu ishuri ry’ubukungu n’ubumenyi bwa politiki i Londres . <ref>https://femmesdumaroc.com/portrait/hind-bensari-lautodidacte-engagee-48352</ref>Yashakanye n'umucuruzi wo muri [[Danemarke]], ubu akaba atuye muri [[Danimarike]].<ref>https://www.dohafilminstitute.com/financing/projects/grants/we-could-be-heroes</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2014, yagarutse muri [[Maroc]] kugirango akore filime ngufi ya documentaire ya mbere yari ''475: Break the Silence'' <ref>https://www.dohafilminstitute.com/financing/projects/grants/we-could-be-heroes</ref>.  Yagize uruhare mu myigaragambyo muri [[Maroc]] kugira ngo ishobore gukuraho itegeko rishya ryemerera abagabo baregwa gufata ku ngufu gushyingiranwa n’abo bahohotewe.<ref>https://www.festivalmarrakech.info/en/personnalite/hind-bensari/</ref> Iyi filime yamamaye cyane mu kinyamakuru New York Times no mu muyoboro wa ARD wo mu Budage ndetse no kuri interineti<ref>https://www.moroccoworldnews.com/2018/05/246273/moroccan-filmmaker-hind-bensari-wins-documentary-award-in-canada</ref>.  yemejeje kandi abayireba kuri TV 2M muri [[Maroc]] kandi isakaza mu bindi bihugu birimo [[Danimarike|Danemark]], [[Porutugali]], [[Kanada]] kandi igurishwa ku miyoboro irenga 20 ku isi. Ni n'umuvugizi wa TEDx<ref>http://www.film-documentaire.fr/4DACTION/w_fiche_film/52327_1</ref><ref>https://womenandhollywood.com/hot-docs-2018-women-directors-meet-hind-bensari-we-could-be-heroes-c09906f8505e/</ref>. 

Ku ya 2 Gicurasi 2018, yasohoye filime ''We Could Be Heroes'' yerekanwe bwa mbere muri 2018 Hot Docs yo muri [[Kanada]] Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime<ref>https://www.moroccoworldnews.com/2018/05/246273/moroccan-filmmaker-hind-bensari-wins-documentary-award-in-canada</ref>. Iyi filime ishingiye ku nkuru y’inshuti ebyiri zamugaye, Azzedine na Youssef, barota kuva muri gereza bakazitabira imikino Paralympique ya Rio.<ref>https://africa.film/we-could-be-heroes-a-hind-bensari-documentary/</ref>  Filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Jury mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Documentaire Hot Docs .  Iyi filime kandi yatsindiye igihembo cyitwa "Best International Documentary Award" mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Toronto, ibaye umukinnyi wa mbere wa Afurika wakiriye igihembo.  Hanyuma film yatsindiye Grand Prix mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Tangier .<ref>https://moroccanladies.com/breaking-news/moroccan-filmmaker-hind-bensari-wins-best-international-documentary-award-in-canada-22010</ref> 

